Corollary term_regular_lx: term_regular lx.
Proof.
  unfold term_regular.
  intros t t' HBx.
  induction HBx.
  - apply term_regular_b_ctx; assumption.
  - apply term_regular_x_ctx; assumption.
Qed.
    
